Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.57,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正准圆_GBK}{\fs26}{\1a&H6E&\1c&H704338&}{\be1}{\pos(300,60)\fad(200,400)\bord0}突破了分組賽了哦！
