Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.77,0:08:34.60,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正准圆_GBK}{\fs26}{\1a&H6E&\1c&H704338&}{\be1}{\pos(600,60)\fad(200,400)\bord0}終於要進行決賽了！
