Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.04,0:08:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背誦時間結束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在比賽開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}なにわずに さくやこのはな ふゆごもり
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}花開難波津 寒冬閉羞顏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北央 取得五戰全勝 哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞 澤 高 中 加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:09:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}いまをはるべと さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:09:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}今兮春滿地 花開香芬芳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞澤原本沒有呼口號的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會不會是剛剛才想到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}いまをはるべと さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}今兮春滿地 花開香芬芳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.39,0:09:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別被這張「千早」給迷惑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要像平常那樣 進攻就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}たちわかれ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下因幡道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.01,0:09:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搶了千早陣地裡的「たま」和「たち」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙也是進攻歌牌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,須籐的S是「不停進攻」的S
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我守住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊也搶到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我領先了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,須籐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然是先拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都丟牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.55,0:09:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在才開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進攻吧 瑞澤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.14,0:09:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進攻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不確定也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.32,0:09:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸出手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進攻敵陣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 真島
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然激動起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.47,0:10:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說你原本就是這種性格嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}まつとしきかば いまかへりこむ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.71,0:10:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}諸君勞久候 幾欲再回還
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進攻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:11.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}かぜをいたみ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:11.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,風急波浪湧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}いまはただ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至此勞空候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直想進攻的 可是牌不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是在自陣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.53,0:10:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:26.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂攻擊歌牌就是進攻敵陣 \N其中有給予對方精神打擊的意味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同時也有送牌讓自陣的配置變得更有利的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.64,0:10:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早 你可別被纏住了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確定每一張牌的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.33,0:10:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亮晃晃的好刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這張「千早」好礙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}つくばねの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仰望築波嶺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易進攻敵陣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 都怪你不說抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:11:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搶到了 搶到了 搶到一張了 繼續加油
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早 連我都在敵陣搶到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼能輸在進攻上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也搶到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.15,0:11:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這邊也守住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下一次一定要搶到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在個人戰的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一張牌也就只是一張牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}こひぞつもりて ふちとなりぬる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}相思積歲月 早已化深潭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要為隊伍搶下一張牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}うかりける
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神前空禱告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搶到了 連續搶到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1}千早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}綾瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 才不是連續搶到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是剛才的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才聽到「う」就出手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明還沒有唸到「うか」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是抱著會手誤的覺悟才出手的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來大家也要搶到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持田 今天的讀手有幾個人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是高中的預賽 所以一直都是由那位女性擔任的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:11:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.76,0:12:01.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 這已經是第五場比賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.96,0:12:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}はげしかれとは いのらぬものを
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.96,0:12:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}初瀨山峰下 偏遭凜冽風
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早 那個讀手的習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的耳朵已經掌握到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}おほえやま
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山長平野闊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 這次真的是連續搶到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早連續搶到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.23,0:12:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.10,0:12:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早開始進入狀態了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道大家的心境開始變得輕鬆起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拿到的一張牌 不是普通的一張牌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要連續搶到3張哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.43,0:12:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算千早掌握了讀手的習慣 但也不是全部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時也是剛好猜中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}まだふみもみず あまのはしだて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}渺杳無音信 幾曾橋立遊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 會在對方的心中留下烙印
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}あしびきの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,野雉深山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會造成失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}註釋：雙重牌：當一方在敵陣拿到牌 而另一方手誤時 得牌方可以送兩張牌給失誤方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 雙重牌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 須…須籐前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:13:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了中斷不利的比賽走向而離席嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個好時機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 果然俯視能讓人冷靜下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北央 一張一張的奪下來噢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}ながながしよを ひとりかもねむ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}浸浸秋夜冷 只恐又獨眠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的反應確實很快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.50,0:13:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}わたのはら こぎいでてみれば ひさかたの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.50,0:13:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茫茫船出海 放眼望天邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}歌牌可不僅僅於此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 被萌上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻入對方敵陣的圍手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新也很擅長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:51.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的手掌也變得那麼大了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.41,0:13:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,移動牌了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.95,0:13:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,移動這種地方？可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是很有趣！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.43,0:14:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別再東想西想了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為那張牌對我來說很特別
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不管在何處都能搶到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.25,0:14:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像磁石一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}わすらるる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有誓遭遺忘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}しらつゆに
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清秋原野上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.41,0:14:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}みかきもり
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.41,0:14:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衛士焚篝火
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早正壓制著他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的差距是幾張
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,13張 一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早追上了北央的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉包君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.76,0:14:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊 綽號是肉包君什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.97,0:14:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是翠北歌牌會的西田同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為你放棄歌牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為都沒出席大賽嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.23,0:14:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明那麼強的說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}ひるはきえつつ ものをこそおもへ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}相思魂杳杳 長夜摧心肝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}このたびは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幣帛未曾帶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甘糟 那由太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在練習會上見到的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.87,0:15:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙還只是初學者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然年長卻比不過我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,優征是個努力的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就能到A級吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.41,0:15:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為A級選手…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.91,0:15:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在幹些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:29.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師也好久沒見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}あはぢしま
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.52,0:15:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淡路來千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:37.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空牌？對不起對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}かくとだに
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊吹艾草茂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以為剛剛的能搶到的說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛是我比較快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 這樣下去 我的小拇指在下面的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣 再這樣 不是在我拇指的上面嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.96,0:15:57.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不知放棄啊 你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:15:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為那真的是我的牌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 這裡就算成自陣的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.59,0:16:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 別這樣 聽我說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.16,0:16:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}もゆるおもひを
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}草木盡枯凋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}みよしのの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故國秋風起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 翻身了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹勁足過頭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.62,0:16:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹得好 西田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉包君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ふるさとさむく ころもうつなり
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寒砧催夜盡 戶戶搗衣衫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.38,0:16:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要贏 我要以我的進攻歌牌來贏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝指教
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝指教
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:17:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北央勝兩場
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還要勝一場
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只要勝一場了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.91,0:17:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,須籐前輩和甘糟前輩的情況都比預想的要棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救這局正是本人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 為什麼這傢伙那麼難纏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一百張中的「や」牌有4張
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「やえ」和「やまざ」已經讀過了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以自陣右邊的2張聽到「や」就一起拍走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「よ」牌中「よのなか」的2張已經讀過了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是「よも」和「よを」還沒有讀到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.31,0:17:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以「よ」出手要慎重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.94,0:17:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「ちぎりお」已經讀過了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「ちぎりき」和「ちは」聽到「ち」就把2張拍走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「な」牌一共8張
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.01,0:17:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「ながら」「ながか」\N「なにし」「なつ」「なにわが」已經讀過了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡就只剩「なげけ」和「なにはえ」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意空牌「なげき」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:17:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好的聽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要上當
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我既不像千早那樣有過人的直覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不像西田那樣能讀懂比賽的走勢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}なげきつつ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘆息無閒暇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「なげき」還沒讀過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.26,0:18:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決勝字的變化我是絕對不會弄錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要成為大家的脊樑骨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}いかにひさしき ものとかはしる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}迢迢怨遙夜 問君安可知
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失誤什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算一次也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}よもすがら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜夜相思苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝指教
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞澤勝一場
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有6張
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:19:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(204,30)}ねやのひまさへ つれなかりけり
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:19:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs34\pos(204,60)}深閨門上縫 黯黯亦無情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:18:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然比到勝負難分的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:19:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自陣的牌絕對不能在這時候被搶走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}なにはえの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難波葦節短
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他剛才是要防守自陣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.09,0:19:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.26,0:19:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.52,0:19:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.18,0:19:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs28}我的夢想也是成為名人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是比賽的順境還是逆境
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教會了我歌牌樂趣的正是老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.30,0:19:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.65,0:19:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞澤勝兩場
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.62,0:19:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好樣的 西田
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.67,0:19:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想帶持田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.00,0:19:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶大家去全國大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.26,0:19:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要贏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\pos(424,440)}ちはやぶる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠悠神代事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝指教
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs27}明明還有「ちぎりき」 竟然聽到「ち」就去搶牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3\fs27}你好厲害 好厲害 綾瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\fs27}她果然睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.01,0:20:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs27}千早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.31,0:20:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這種情況下為什麼她還能那樣搶牌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的眼神已經沒有了想贏的念頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.93,0:21:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新 你以前不發郵件的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要去全國大賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.66,0:21:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 新 他們是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.53,0:21:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來近江神宮看我們吧 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.26,0:01:49.54,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}帰り道は過ぎていく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.66,0:01:52.92,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}少し風が吹いている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.02,0:01:58.09,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}たわいない会話妙に楽しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:02.97,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}今でも変わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:06.71,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}僕ら待ち合わせたあの場所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:12.08,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}君はまだ覚えてるのかな?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:19.92,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}今はちはやふる想い胸に抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:25.26,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}目指した先に何があるんだ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.36,0:02:31.04,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}今なら掴めそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.12,0:02:33.92,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}手を伸ばしてみる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:40.45,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}夢の途中きっといつかまた会えるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.26,0:01:49.54,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}慢步走過回家的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.66,0:01:52.92,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}微風輕輕吹拂著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.02,0:01:58.09,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}閒話家常也異常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.51,0:02:02.97,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}至今依舊一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:06.71,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}我們常常相約等候的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:12.08,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}你可否仍然記得呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:19.92,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}現在我心懷強烈的嚮往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:25.26,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}有什麼在目標之處
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.36,0:02:31.04,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}現在的話似乎能抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.12,0:02:33.92,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}試著伸出雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:40.45,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}在夢想的路上終有一天會再度重逢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:29.24,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}行くあてない街
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.41,0:21:34.52,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}ひとり先を歩く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.32,0:21:39.77,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}夕日に照らされた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:44.84,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}失いそうな心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.17,0:21:49.99,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}変わってゆくなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.25,0:21:54.73,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}想いもしなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.65,0:22:00.01,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}君と重ねた夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.19,0:22:05.02,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}いつの間に違う方へと
